WEBVTT

06:59.000 --> 07:00.458
Good morning, sir.

09:24.083 --> 09:26.708
Don't ask me anything.
Don't ask me nothing.

09:27.625 --> 09:31.583
Boy, I don't want to hear anything.

09:35.166 --> 09:38.333
Mom, I left Thandeka with Minata.

09:38.416 --> 09:42.166
Okay, my boy. I'll be late tonight.

09:42.250 --> 09:44.333
Don't forget to pick her up.

09:44.416 --> 09:46.333
