09:50.458 --> 09:52.833
Bring her home by six, period.

09:55.583 --> 09:57.458
Hey, dawg, let's try there.

09:57.541 --> 09:59.625
-It's a waste of time, man.
-Let's go.

10:01.500 --> 10:04.541
Oh, this child. I'm telling you, my child.

10:05.041 --> 10:06.833
-Good morning, sir.
-Yes, my boy.

10:06.916 --> 10:09.458
I'm looking for a job.

10:11.000 --> 10:12.375
