Look at me right now. I'm stressed.
I can't look after my mom and my sister.

14:54.375 --> 14:57.083
This is why you'll end up
selling crystal meth.

14:57.166 --> 14:58.583
What else can I do?

14:59.250 --> 15:01.083
I'll be supplying the whole world.

15:01.166 --> 15:03.791
We will be rich.
We'll be making money. You'll see.

15:04.541 --> 15:06.041
Weed, boy.

15:06.125 --> 15:07.541
