18:35.458 --> 18:36.291
Here.

19:39.916 --> 19:42.708
There's no reason to worry about the box.

19:42.791 --> 19:44.583
Everyone kept their word.

19:47.125 --> 19:52.875
True, but the higher-ups
had to pull a few more favors than usual.

19:53.708 --> 19:55.708
You know your package is huge.

20:01.666 --> 20:05.583
