the construction of the school.

20:07.666 --> 20:09.291
You know which one.

20:17.208 --> 20:20.083
What can I say? It's a big package.

20:31.125 --> 20:34.041
Jeez. What's making you smile like this?

20:34.708 --> 20:36.583
It's nothing.

20:36.666 --> 20:37.958
-Relax.
-What is it?

20:38.041 --> 20:39.458
Is it Given?

20:40.375 --> 20:41.958
No.

21:31.500 --> 21:33.333
Dad, please calm down.

22:17.125 --> 22:18.333
How much did we make?

22:26.000 --> 22:27.833
It's going to be fine, Dad. Don't worry.

22:29.041 --> 22:31.833
You know what? We should go home.

22:31.916 --> 22:34.250
I'll fix you that pasta dish
Mom used to make.

22:35.125 --> 22:39.250
Now you're talking.
With that tasty cream sauce?

22:40.875 --> 22:42.833
Let's get the keys and leave, my girl.

22:45.291 --> 22:47.916
It's going to work out.
Everything works out.

22:49.875 --> 22:51.000
There.

22:51.083 --> 22:55.666
This right here is the perfect place.

22:55.750 --> 22:58.583
Dad, we have our own place.

22:58.666 --> 23:00.166
And we're barely making rent.

23:00.250 --> 23:02.708
The problem is that you have no vision.

23:02.791 --> 23:06.750
This place will help this entire block.

23:06.833 --> 23:10.208
Since when did you start
thinking about expanding? Dad.

23:14.750 --> 23:17.416
This has been my dream for you.

23:18.875 --> 23:20.291
It's going to become a reality.

23:59.375 --> 24:02.625
Palesa, what did I say to you
about mixing with these people?

24:02.708 --> 24:05.541
Please don't start with that.
These people are not the same.

24:06.708 --> 24:08.750
Look at how our stores are suffering.

24:08.833 --> 24:13.833
Because of these people
who are selling stolen goods for cheap.

24:15.333 --> 24:19.166
These people are worse
than what white people did to us.

24:19.750 --> 24:21.208
That's what they said about you.

27:20.833 --> 27:22.750
This is what I'm talking about.

27:23.791 --> 27:27.041
This is how it should be.
The men need to be strong.

28:56.458 --> 28:57.875
Hey there, girl.

28:59.083 --> 29:01.500
Why are you avoiding me?

29:01.583 --> 29:03.166
I'm not avoiding you, Given.

29:03.250 --> 29:04.916
Yes, you are.

29:05.000 --> 29:08.583
Look, I can take care of you
and your family.

29:09.208 --> 29:10.208
I'm serious.

29:10.791 --> 29:15.208
I can make your problems disappear,
and all the stress you might have.

29:15.291 --> 29:18.375
You know I don't want
to get married, right? To anyone.

29:22.541 --> 29:24.875
-What's the matter, Dad?
-Please get out.

29:24.958 --> 29:26.166
I need to speak to Given.

29:26.750 --> 29:28.625
-No, what's the matter?
-Get out!

29:29.333 --> 29:30.416
Get out!

31:25.750 --> 31:26.875
Hello, Mother.

31:29.083 --> 31:31.625
Do you see it? I made it for you.

31:32.291 --> 31:33.208
Oh, wow.

31:38.333 --> 31:40.291
-Is it an elephant?
-An elephant?

31:40.958 --> 31:43.291
Where have you seen an elephant like that?

31:43.375 --> 31:45.625
Stop being an idiot.

31:46.750 --> 31:49.083
Tell me.

31:49.708 --> 31:54.500
I hear rumors all over this place

31:56.250 --> 32:00.666
that my son, who I raised with respect

32:01.666 --> 32:06.041
and dignity, is killing people.

32:06.125 --> 32:08.750
No, Mother, don't worry about rumors.

32:10.875 --> 32:13.000
You must always remember that

32:13.083 --> 32:15.666
there's no man
who is an island in this world.

32:15.750 --> 32:18.250
Yes, I hear you, Mother.

32:18.333 --> 32:21.500
You've always been a good boy

32:22.791 --> 32:24.666
who has respect.

32:24.750 --> 32:27.791
Now I'm begging you, my son.

32:28.375 --> 32:30.000
Please be smart.

32:32.958 --> 32:35.000
I will keep it right here.

32:35.625 --> 32:36.583
See?

32:37.750 --> 32:39.458
It's going to keep me safe.

32:48.000 --> 32:49.000
It's okay.

32:49.958 --> 32:53.375
Tell me, are you going to
come and see me tomorrow?

32:57.458 --> 32:59.375
I'll come and see you.

33:50.666 --> 33:52.208
The duck is delicious.

34:05.458 --> 34:06.416
…still battling?

34:10.916 --> 34:15.375
I hope it's not like the last two weeks.

35:23.750 --> 35:26.833
Hey, the truck is ready.

35:27.541 --> 35:28.833
Ball's in your court now.

36:29.958 --> 36:34.041
Hey, Wiseman. It's Given.

36:35.541 --> 36:36.791
Tell me,

36:36.875 --> 36:40.791
how long has Palesa
been seeing that fool Adze?

36:40.875 --> 36:42.250
What are you saying?

36:42.333 --> 36:45.625
I saw her together with that idiot.

36:46.583 --> 36:50.875
You know what?
To hell with the both of them.

36:51.666 --> 36:53.375
All right, Wiseman.

38:20.791 --> 38:22.958
Follow me to my office.

38:34.166 --> 38:37.250
Your friend has gotten himself
a nice job here in my club.

38:37.333 --> 38:38.916
Thank you, Bra Sol.

38:40.708 --> 38:42.666
I almost didn't.

38:49.125 --> 38:50.875
So, what are you going to do for me?

38:50.958 --> 38:53.958
Anything you want me to do,
Bra Sol, I will do it.

38:56.333 --> 38:58.666
I only work with people I can trust.

39:00.750 --> 39:02.541
You can trust me.

39:02.625 --> 39:05.958
Just give me a chance,
and let me show you that you can trust me.

39:08.541 --> 39:11.708
That white girl you came with…

39:12.416 --> 39:13.500
She's really sexy.

39:15.458 --> 39:16.791
She is…

39:19.000 --> 39:20.583
She's my friend's girlfriend.

39:23.500 --> 39:28.041
I need girls like her in my club.
That are sexy.

39:33.250 --> 39:36.500
Do you think you'll be able
to help me with that?

39:36.583 --> 39:39.083
As you know, one hand washes the other.

39:40.166 --> 39:42.666
I don't know about that, Bra Sol.

39:44.958 --> 39:48.541
White people took everything from you.

39:49.625 --> 39:52.541
They took your father from you.
Do you remember?

39:58.083 --> 40:00.083
You'll make yourself some money.

40:07.208 --> 40:08.541
I won't disappoint you.

40:08.625 --> 40:10.458
I know you won't let me down.

40:12.458 --> 40:15.833
Go and have fun in the club.

40:24.666 --> 40:25.833
So long, Bra Sol.

42:13.458 --> 42:14.750
Hello, neighbors.

42:15.500 --> 42:17.416
I just spoke to the landlord.

42:17.500 --> 42:20.041
He said he has rented out
that place already.

42:20.125 --> 42:22.125
He gave it to that Nigerian, Adze.

42:22.208 --> 42:25.583
He says he gave him an offer
he couldn't refuse.

42:25.666 --> 42:29.041
-The guy who stays by your apartment?
-That is my shop, man.

42:29.125 --> 42:34.291
It doesn't belong to anybody else.
Listen, I'm sure he used drug money.

42:34.375 --> 42:35.875
Right now, he's busy unpacking.

42:35.958 --> 42:40.291
This is ridiculous. We're being undermined
in our own neighborhood.

42:40.375 --> 42:43.125
Gents, these foreigners
are not here to play.

42:43.208 --> 42:45.708
They are here to make us starve.

42:45.791 --> 42:49.666
They are bringing in expired food,
and they're selling it at half price.

42:49.750 --> 42:51.458
They're making our people sick.

42:51.541 --> 42:54.083
Next thing,
they'll be selling drugs to our kids.

42:54.916 --> 42:58.416
And then they'll sell them off
as prostitutes.

42:58.500 --> 43:01.125
Listen up, gents.

43:01.208 --> 43:05.625
I'm saying, Nigerians and Zimbabweans
are all the same.

43:05.708 --> 43:06.916
They're full of shit.

43:07.000 --> 43:11.375
They are all the same.
That's why we need to show them who's who.

43:11.458 --> 43:12.375
Do you get me?

43:12.458 --> 43:17.333
These people must go back
to wherever they came from.

43:22.041 --> 43:23.666
They must go back!

43:26.791 --> 43:29.583
They must go!

43:46.208 --> 43:48.791
This is Bra Sol's stuff, man.

45:11.791 --> 45:12.916
We can go now.

52:01.208 --> 52:04.833
-Where's your Uber, man?
-Relax, it's coming.

52:18.583 --> 52:21.583
