57:58.625 --> 58:02.250
That man promised me a lot of money.

58:02.333 --> 58:03.208
Who?

58:03.291 --> 58:04.625
Who do you think?

58:06.375 --> 58:08.500
I told you to stay away from that man.

58:12.041 --> 58:13.583
You hit me hard, man.

58:14.291 --> 58:17.750
He said he wants your girl
to work at the club.

58:18.541 --> 58:19.958
Where is she now?

58:21.208 --> 58:22.041
I don't know.

58:23.333 --> 58:25.166
-I don't know.
-Give me her dad's number.

1:00:47.875 --> 1:00:50.791
-Hi, Dad.
-I see what you're up to.

1:00:51.500 --> 1:00:53.833
You chose him after they stole from us.

1:00:54.416 --> 1:00:56.291
-Dad, no.
-Don't "Dad" me.

1:00:56.375 --> 1:00:58.500
Listen, I saw you with that Nigerian.

1:00:58.583 --> 1:01:00.083
Are you not ashamed?

1:01:00.833 --> 1:01:03.666
Dad, Adze didn't steal anything from you.

1:01:05.083 --> 1:01:06.625
Hey, don't you dare.

1:01:06.708 --> 1:01:09.166
You're telling me
that I was not fast enough?

1:01:09.250 --> 1:01:12.625
After you just broke up with Given.

1:01:12.708 --> 1:01:14.541
Now you're with a Nigerian.

1:01:14.625 --> 1:01:17.541
You know what?
I never thought that one day

1:01:17.625 --> 1:01:20.458
my daughter would be
the prostitute of this place.

1:01:24.583 --> 1:01:27.083
Where are you going?
I want you here tonight!

1:01:27.166 --> 1:01:29.333
Hey, if I see you again
with that foreigner…

1:05:26.458 --> 1:05:27.541
It's okay.

1:05:28.333 --> 1:05:29.250
Relax.

1:05:31.416 --> 1:05:33.208
Payment's in, man.

1:05:34.208 --> 1:05:38.541
Your million rand for those 50 girls
and then my 400,000 rand.

1:05:42.416 --> 1:05:46.333
I told you your stupid school idea
was a bad one.

1:05:46.416 --> 1:05:47.833
It's too close to home.

1:05:57.833 --> 1:05:59.833
Bring it here. Let's see.

1:06:03.000 --> 1:06:05.750
Oh, she's really pretty.

1:06:08.583 --> 1:06:09.916
How much?

1:06:16.666 --> 1:06:18.458
You are a trusted man.

1:06:19.625 --> 1:06:22.000
Let's close it off at 100,000 rand.

1:06:28.750 --> 1:06:31.041
This country is so rotten.

1:06:40.333 --> 1:06:42.250
I hear you, man.

1:06:43.250 --> 1:06:44.708
Look after your boys.

1:06:44.791 --> 1:06:48.125
I will give you all your money
after I get that whore.

1:07:08.000 --> 1:07:10.875
So long, man.

1:07:20.375 --> 1:07:21.250
Come in.

1:07:25.791 --> 1:07:27.041
What brings you here?

1:07:27.125 --> 1:07:29.166
My money for Nicki.

1:07:29.250 --> 1:07:32.000
You'll get it
when those girls get shipped off.

1:07:32.083 --> 1:07:33.875
Get shipped off? To where?

1:07:35.041 --> 1:07:36.375
-Overseas.
-Over…

1:07:36.958 --> 1:07:38.500
You didn't mention that to me.

1:07:39.125 --> 1:07:40.958
I don't have to tell you shit.

1:07:41.666 --> 1:07:44.250
You're screwing me over now, Bra Sol.

1:07:44.333 --> 1:07:45.750
Did you tell someone?

1:07:48.583 --> 1:07:50.000
I can see you're lying.

1:07:52.708 --> 1:07:55.416
I hope for your little sister's sake
you're not lying to me.

1:07:55.958 --> 1:07:59.125
I make a lot of money with little girls.
Do you get me?

1:08:01.583 --> 1:08:05.000
Bra Sol, I can't betray my friend.

1:08:05.708 --> 1:08:09.583
I'm sure there's another way
we can make money.

1:08:11.541 --> 1:08:13.500
There is something we can do.

1:08:15.000 --> 1:08:18.125
We need to call her father
and ask for a ransom.

1:08:20.083 --> 1:08:22.583
You collect that money and bring it to me.

1:08:22.666 --> 1:08:24.666
Then you get the girl back.

1:08:25.416 --> 1:08:29.041
It won't work.

1:08:29.125 --> 1:08:32.166
The shipment is departing in two hours.

1:10:15.333 --> 1:10:16.791
Tell them the truth, man.

1:12:16.666 --> 1:12:18.125
What are they saying?

1:12:22.583 --> 1:12:24.041
Step on it, Thando.

1:12:28.416 --> 1:12:31.208
Our mother

1:12:31.291 --> 1:12:34.708
Our mother

1:12:34.791 --> 1:12:36.791
Our mother

1:12:38.208 --> 1:12:40.583
GET LOST

