Our mother

1:12:49.208 --> 1:12:52.166
-Hush, don't cry
-Our mother

1:12:52.791 --> 1:12:56.666
-Wipe your tears
-Our mother

1:12:56.750 --> 1:13:00.041
Our mother

1:13:00.125 --> 1:13:02.416
Our mother

1:13:03.166 --> 1:13:05.250
Our mother

1:13:48.708 --> 1:13:51.083
Our mother

1:13:51.833 --> 1:13:53.166
Our mother

1:13:55.875 --> 1:13:57.250
Listen up, soldiers!

1:13:58.041 --> 1:14:00.625
We are here now, right?

1:14:12.000 --> 1:14:14.291
-To hell with the foreigners!
-To hell!

1:14:14.375 --> 1:14:15.875
-Salute to the soldiers!
-Salute!

1:14:27.625 --> 1:14:30.541
-To hell with foreigners!
-To hell!

1:18:23.125 --> 1:18:25.333
Listen up.
Some of you must take this corner,

1:18:25.416 --> 1:18:28.375
while others take this side
and lock them inside.

1:18:28.458 --> 1:18:31.666
Salute, soldiers! Let's go!

1:19:17.958 --> 1:19:21.125
Gents, this idiot is inside.

1:19:21.208 --> 1:19:23.791
We need to show him who we truly are.

1:19:23.875 --> 1:19:27.333
I want you to box him in from that side.

1:19:27.416 --> 1:19:29.375
Let's show them
who's the boss here. Right?

1:20:06.708 --> 1:20:10.166
Let's go. Lock him in.
We don't have time for this.

1:20:54.750 --> 1:20:57.000
What do you say? Should we do this?

1:21:17.666 --> 1:21:18.958
Hi, Bra Sol.

1:21:19.875 --> 1:21:21.750
It's me, Thando.

1:21:24.333 --> 1:21:26.416
Yes, the deal is on now.

1:21:28.333 --> 1:21:30.916
Yes, he's bringing
the whole half a million.

1:21:34.916 --> 1:21:38.125
You know that guy… I'm good at my job,

1:21:38.208 --> 1:21:41.583
so I got there and told him
